overview: From a cat fight with Lindsay to a love affair with David, Jesse, Chris, Simon, Danny and Doug, Jasmine Waltz has been dubbed the Hollywood "it" girl on Howard Stern. The most beautiful woman to ever be in a celebrity sex scandal DVD, bar none! Her hardcore Valentine's Day gift to her boyfriend was lost and now it's found! Take a peek inside Hollywood's bedroom and see why Jasmine is the stars favorite "it" girl!
title: Jasmine Waltz Hollywood It Girl
